data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Naples! This impressive 2021-built residence, located in prestigious Golden Gate Estates, sits on 1.59 fully fenced acres with a spacious entrance, perfect for trucks and more. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and high ceilings, this home features impact-resistant doors and windows throughout. The property's clean, well-leveled patio offers an ideal outdoor space for tranquility. This unique opportunity boasts a mother suite, a modern osmosis water system, and even a dedicated office space. Additionally, it comes complete with a two-car garage for your convenience. Combining luxury, location, and lifestyle, this remarkable property represents the best that Naples, FL has to offer. Don't miss the chance to make this immaculate house your home. Schedule a viewing today and envision your Florida dream lifestyle in this extraordinary residence.
